OL,3,CTeenager, 18, pleads guilty to
OL,4,Cmurdering his mother
OL,6,FA teenager has pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fmurdering his mother.
OL,9,FTristan Thomas Roberts appeared at
OL,10,FMold Crown Court to admit the charge
OL,11,Fof murdering Angela Jane Shellis.
OL,13,FThe 18-year-old, of Coniston Drive,
OL,14,FPrestatyn, murdered Ms Shellis, 45, on
OL,15,FOctober 24 last year. She was found
OL,16,Fdead in undergrowth beside a footpath
OL,17,Fnear Prestatyn's Morfa Nature Reserve
OL,18,Fby a member of the public.
