OL,6,FThe judge, His Honour Rhys Rowlands,
OL,7,Fadjourned proceedings until a
OL,8,Fsentencing hearing on March 25.
OL,10,FHe said: "There can only be one
OL,11,Fsentence for the offence of murder.
OL,12,FThe fact you have pleaded guilty will
OL,13,Fbe reflected in the sentence."
OL,15,FA provisional trial date had been set
OL,16,Ffor March 16 this year. The defendant,
OL,17,Fwho has shoulder-length black hair,
OL,18,Fwore a blue jumper and dark trousers
OL,19,Fin the glass-fronted dock during the
OL,20,Fhearing.
