OL,6,FHe said: "Angela was a valued member
OL,7,Fof staff, who joined the Rhyl High
OL,8,Fteam in 2023 and was a caring and
OL,9,Fcommitted teaching assistant. We are
OL,10,Fdeeply upset as a school community and
OL,11,Fhold Angela's family and friends
OL,12,Fforemost in our thoughts, as they try
OL,13,Fto come to terms with their loss."
